## 10. Decision Hierarchy

Mandatory engineering order — **implementation shall never bypass this order:**

```
Requirements
    ↓
Architecture
    ↓
Interfaces
    ↓
Qualification
    ↓
Implementation
    ↓
Testing
    ↓
Optimization
```

| Stage | Owner | Output |
|-------|-------|--------|
| Requirements | Architect / SRS | REQ-* IDs, work package scope |
| Architecture | Architect | ADR, EDL, docs/001–009 |
| Interfaces | Architect + Implementation | DCP, DCPI, YAML schema, module map |
| Qualification | Implementation + Reviewer | `hardware/qualification/` records |
| Implementation | Implementation Engineer | Code, configs, docs per WP |
| Testing | Implementation + Reviewer | Verified results, DevKit gate |
| Optimization | After verification only | Performance, cost — not before evidence |

