## 20. Mandatory Completion Report

At task end, provide:

1. Task Summary  
2. Files Created  
3. Files Modified  
4. Validation Performed — include exact commands/procedures and **actual results**; reference evidence IDs or locations  
5. Acceptance Criteria (PASS / FAIL / PARTIAL / NOT VERIFIED)  
6. Open Questions  
7. Risks and Observations (or Architectural Decisions Required)  
8. Out-of-Scope Recommendations (or Improvement Suggestions — do not implement)  
9. Final Status: Ready for Review · Blocked · Partially Complete · Failed Validation  

Where applicable, also reference: impact classification (Level 0 / 1 / 2); Change Impact Analysis ID or Lightweight Impact Note; Verification Evidence IDs; Review Handoff Package ID; commit SHA and revision identity used for validation.

Work packages may specify additional sections (e.g. Architect Review Package).

Template: `docs/templates/Work_Package_Template.md`.  
Filled records: `docs/records/`.

