## 22. Continuous Improvement

| Practice | Requirement |
|----------|-------------|
| Record lessons | Open questions and risks in completion reports |
| Propose constitution updates | Via Architect Review Package — not silent edits |
| Supersede decisions | ADR/EDL supersession — never delete history |
| WP feedback | Recurring problems → constitution amendment proposal |
| Checklist maintenance | `agents_stuff/DOC_CHECKLIST.md` tracks doc debt — not normative |

Implementation Engineer may **suggest** improvements; System Architect **approves** policy changes.

